com.cloudera.director.aws.rds

Class RDSEndpoints

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cloudera.director.aws.rds.RDSEndpoints
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.google.common.base.Function<String,String>

    public class RDSEndpoints
extends Object
implements com.google.common.base.Function<String,String>
    A lookup mechanism for RDS endpoints. Unlike EC2, RDS does not provide a means through the API to discover endpoints. This class looks up endpoints using a built-in list and an override list that the user can easily modify.
